OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FPeak rail fares scrapped as
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fsix-month trial begins     
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Peak-time rail fares have been scrapped
OL,6, on ScotRail services from Monday as    
OL,7, part of a six-month pilot scheme.      
OL,9,FThe cost of a rush hour ticket between 
OL,10,FGlasgow and Edinburgh has almost halved
OL,11,Fin an initiative aimed at boosting rail
OL,12,Ftravel.                                
OL,14,FScotRail has warned customers that     
OL,15,Ftrains may be busier than usual during 
OL,16,Fthe Scottish government-funded pilot.  
OL,18,FAdditional carriages have been added to
OL,19,Fsome services, and the operator said it
OL,20,Fwould be monitoring the situation.     
